This paper is primarily focused on image classification, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also discusses the challenges of reducing latency variance in cloud deployments, which is related to distributed computing (cs.DC). The proposed Collage-CNN model is a machine learning model, which falls under the machine learning (cs.LG) sub-category. The paper also discusses the use of load balancers and redundancy coding, which are related to distributed systems (cs.DS) and control systems (cs.SY) sub-categories, respectively.
